summary: An Ordinance providing for the purchasing of the south one-half (S. 1/2) of the southwest one-fourth (S.W. 1/4) of the northeast one-fourth (N.E. 1/4) of Section Twenty-four (24), Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Three (3) East, W. M., at a price not to exceed Four Thousand Dollars ($4,000.00) per acre, for park and parkway purposes.
